criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Had being aged 55-70 years;

          -  Female;

          -  Post-menopausal;

          -  Sedentary (not practicing physical exercise for at least 6 months).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic kidney diseases;

          -  Infectious contagious diseases;

          -  Coronary heart disease;

          -  Smokers

          -  Alcoholics.
